name: MENS. Hermans R. Nafty for Rossmore.
description:
Hermans says, " Get Nafty ! "

My men's line is a cool collabo with my dear artist friend Hermans R. Nafty. He is a man about town on both coasts.  A rock star of sorts, even if only to him and me. He long suffers from burn out from his partying days, but we don't tell him because we like him that way, faded everlasting and successful beyond belief!! No remorse. No remorse.

Dapper, masculine, cool, he'd never wear jewelry. . . but there is just something about this piece...

Love's it. Wears it. Never takes it off. >>We likeeeee.

So, there you have it. Hermans R. Nafty for Rossmore.

get one. get there. & don't ask him what his middle name is!!!

name: the radness.
description:
all variations -custom made-to-order ONLY >> Allow 1-4 wks.

do you ever look around, and feel like things are one color?
or that the volume around you seems to be turned down low?

and then wish you had a way to turn up the charge on everything?

throw a bolt into your life with this little trinket!

find ~the radness~ everywhere you turn, when you decide to live in the extraordinary electricity of the present moment...

~layers well with the other Rossmore. bits, in that it will electrify
and amplify any piece, this necklace 'turns it up a notch', ya know...

this is the piece to get when you want to remind your self to always strive for the phenomenal and great, even in the mundane; whether it's in the way you pour yourself a cup of delicious coffee everyday, or cut out heart shapes with scissors! lol, or whether it's in training for a marathon. whatever your speed, just do it with passion, and quality, and you will find a source of freedom just in the enjoyment of that excellence:)

yayy. xoxo S
